OL,3,CMark Drakeford named Wales' health
OL,4,Csecretary in Eluned Morgan's cabinet
OL,6,FMark Drakeford will take over as
OL,7,FWales' health secretary in First
OL,8,FMinister Eluned Morgan's Welsh
OL,9,FGovernment cabinet, it has been
OL,10,Fannounced.
OL,12,FThe former first minister will take on
OL,13,Fthe health and social care brief on an
OL,14,Finterim basis, inheriting the role
OL,15,Fwhich Ms Morgan had held since 2021.
