OL,4,Csecretary in Eluned Morgan's cabinet
OL,6,FThe new FM has also confirmed that Huw
OL,7,FIrranca-Davies MS becomes deputy first
OL,8,Fminister alongside his role as climate
OL,9,Fchange and rural affairs secretary,
OL,10,Fwhile Ms Morgan retains cabinet
OL,11,Fresponsibility for the Welsh language.
OL,13,FElisabeth Jones, a former chief legal
OL,14,Fadviser for the National Assembly for
OL,15,FWales and Senedd, has also been
OL,16,Fappointed Counsel General on an
OL,17,Finterim basis.
