OL,3,CMark Drakeford named Wales' health
OL,4,Csecretary in Eluned Morgan's cabinet
OL,6,FMr Drakeford stepped down from the top
OL,7,Fjob in March, and was succeeded by
OL,8,FVaughan Gething, who resigned after a
OL,9,Fturbulent four months in charge to
OL,10,Fpave the way for Ms Morgan becoming
OL,11,Fleader of Welsh Labour and the new
OL,12,Ffirst minister of Wales, the first
OL,13,Fwoman to do so in its 25-year history.
OL,15,FThe end to Mr Gething's reign was
OL,16,Fescalated when four members of his
OL,17,Fcabinet resigned on the same day in
OL,18,FJuly: they were cabinet members Mick
OL,19,FAntoniw, Lesley Griffiths, Julie James
OL,20,Fand Jeremy Miles, who all called for
OL,21,Fhim to quit.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
