OL,4,Csecretary in Eluned Morgan's cabinet
OL,6,FA further cabinet reshuffle is due to
OL,7,Ffollow in September.
OL,9,FMs Morgan said in a written statement:
OL,10,F"The appointments I am announcing
OL,11,Ftoday will provide stability and
OL,12,Fcontinuity over the summer in the
OL,13,Fministerial team... Further
OL,14,Fannouncements on portfolio allocations
OL,15,Fwill be made in September following a
OL,16,Flistening exercise over the summer
OL,17,Fwith the Welsh public. This exercise
OL,18,Fwill help to determine the Welsh
OL,19,FGovernment's priorities and the
OL,20,Fstructure of government for the next
OL,21,F18 months."
