OL,4,Csecretary in Eluned Morgan's cabinet
OL,6,FWelsh Conservatives leader Andrew RT
OL,7,FDavies said: "The show-business of a
OL,8,Freshuffle lasts for a day, and this
OL,9,Fnew government will be judged on their
OL,10,Fresults.
OL,12,F"What Wales needs is a government that
OL,13,Fcan be a voice for all of Wales, and
OL,14,Fcan deliver the NHS and the public
OL,15,Fservices Wales deserves.
OL,17,F"After months of chaos in Welsh
OL,18,FGovernment, Wales will be watching."
