OL,6,FHe added: "What we can be sure of is
OL,7,Fthat the return of Mark Drakeford to
OL,8,Fcabinet, the architect of 20mph, means
OL,9,Fthat 20mph is here to stay in Wales,
OL,10,Fwhich will disappoint motorists and
OL,11,Fbusinesses across Wales.
OL,13,F"The only way to scrap Labour's barmy
OL,14,F20mph speed limit is to vote for the
OL,15,FWelsh Conservatives."
