OL,3,CMark Drakeford named Wales' health
OL,4,Csecretary in Eluned Morgan's cabinet
OL,6,F"At a time of crisis for the Welsh
OL,7,FNHS, the last thing we need is an
OL,8,Finterim health minister that will only
OL,9,Fadd to the uncertainty facing our
OL,10,Fhealth service.
OL,12,F"When previously in post, Mark
OL,13,FDrakeford presided over an 11%
OL,14,Fincrease in those waiting for
OL,15,Ftreatment and Wales' largest health
OL,16,Fboard was put into special measures.
OL,18,F"Wales deserves better than a
OL,19,Fgovernment of stagnation and
OL,20,Findecision.
